    "title": "Anna University is Hiring: Subject Matter Expert (Lead)",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Anna University. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Subject Matter Expert to strengthen our Jabalpur-based team.\n\nAbout Anna University:\nAnna University is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in Zoom/Teams\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Anna University!",
